## 🔐 Task 10: ConfigMap & Secrets

### ConfigMap (non-sensitive):
```yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: iot-config
data:
  KAFKA_BOOTSTRAP: "kafka-0.kafka.iot-infra.svc:9092,kafka-1.kafka.iot-infra.svc:9092,kafka-2.kafka.iot-infra.svc:9092"
  POSTGRES_HOST: "postgres.iot-infra.svc"
  POSTGRES_DB: "iot_platform"
  INFLUXDB_URL: "http://influxdb.iot-infra.svc:8086"
  INFLUXDB_ORG: "iot"
  INFLUXDB_BUCKET: "telemetry"
  MONGODB_URI: "mongodb://mongodb.iot-infra.svc:27017/iot_platform"
  BROKER_PORT: "1883"
```

### Secrets (sensitive — use sealed-secrets in production):
```yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: Secret
metadata:
  name: iot-secrets
type: Opaque
stringData:
  POSTGRES_PASSWORD: "<change-me>"
  INFLUXDB_TOKEN: "<change-me>"
  MONGODB_PASSWORD: "<change-me>"
  JWT_SECRET: "<change-me>"
```

