## 🌐 Task 15: Ingress Configuration

```yaml
apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: iot-ingress
  namespace: iot-app
  annotations:
    nginx.ingress.kubernetes.io/rewrite-target: /
spec:
  ingressClassName: nginx
  rules:
    - host: 203.154.11.226.nip.io
      http:
        paths:
          - path: /api
            pathType: Prefix
            backend:
              service:
                name: iot-backend
                port:
                  number: 8000
          - path: /
            pathType: Prefix
            backend:
              service:
                name: web-app
                port:
                  number: 80
```

> [!WARNING]
> The broker gateway uses a **LoadBalancer** service (not Ingress) since ESP32 devices connect via raw TCP on port 1883, not HTTP.

