## ⚙️ Task 11-12: CI/CD Pipeline

### CI Workflow (`.github/workflows/ci.yml`)

```
On: push, pull_request

Jobs:
  1. lint-test (matrix: [iot-backend, pubsub-broker, telemetry-worker, ttl-cleanup-worker])
     - Install Python 3.12
     - pip install -r requirements.txt
     - ruff check .          (style)
     - mypy .                (types)
     - pytest --cov          (tests + coverage)

  2. lint-test-frontend
     - npm ci
     - npm run lint          (eslint)
     - npm run test          (vitest)

  3. build-push (needs: lint-test, lint-test-frontend)
     - docker build each service
     - docker push to ghcr.io/<org>/iot-<service>:<commit-sha>

  4. security-scan (needs: build-push)
     - trivy image scan each image
     - BLOCK if HIGH/CRITICAL CVEs found
```

### CD Workflow (`.github/workflows/cd.yml`)

```
On: push to main (after CI passes)

Jobs:
  1. deploy-staging
     - kustomize edit set image to commit SHA
     - kubectl apply -k k8s/overlays/staging
     - kubectl rollout status

  2. integration-tests (needs: deploy-staging)
     - pytest tests/integration/ (httpx against staging API)

  3. deploy-production (needs: integration-tests)
     - environment: production (MANUAL APPROVAL required)
     - kustomize edit set image to same commit SHA
     - kubectl apply -k k8s/overlays/production
     - smoke test
     - auto-rollback if smoke fails
```

